{"tid":2361090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英衛生大臣期望抗疫有足夠進展可於3月底放寬限制措施","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:02:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb00b959b53e2b564baa74ea11f85603858c9c68","tid":2361090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569655-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569655-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=464305e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569655-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=727e898d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569655-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國衛生大臣夏國賢說，期望在抗疫方面取得足夠進展，能於3月底放寬限制措施。<br />\n<br />\n夏國賢說，現時每日為超過20萬名國民接種疫苗，正按計劃邁向每星期為200萬人接種的目標。他又說80歲以上組別，約三分一人已獲注射疫苗，顯示計劃取得實質進展，今個星期有大型接種中心開始運作。<br />\n<br />\n英國確診人數突破300萬，超過8萬人死亡。夏國賢說，醫療系統正面對非常困難的處境。"}]}